---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AffiliateCTA from '../../components/AffiliateCTA.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
import { AFFILIATE_LINKS as affiliates } from '../../config/affiliate-links';

const title = 'Fastest AI Website Builders (2025) - Speed Comparison';
const description = 'Which AI builder generates sites fastest? Durable wins at 30 seconds. I timed them all. Detailed speed comparison.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold mb-4">CATEGORY</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Fastest AI Website Builders</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Need a site NOW? Here are the speed champions, ranked by actual generation time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Speed Rankings</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Durable:</strong> ~30 seconds (FASTEST)</li>
        <li><strong>Mixo:</strong> ~30-45 seconds</li>
        <li><strong>Hostinger AI:</strong> ~45-60 seconds</li>
        <li><strong>Dorik:</strong> ~60 seconds</li>
        <li><strong>10Web AI:</strong> ~60-90 seconds</li>
        <li><strong>Wix ADI:</strong> ~90 seconds</li>
        <li><strong>Squarespace Blueprint:</strong> ~2-3 minutes</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Durable - The Speed King</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">30 Seconds From Prompt to Site</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Durable is genuinely fast. Enter your business name and description, and in under a minute you have a complete website with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-2">
            <li>Multiple pages (home, about, services, contact)</li>
            <li>AI-written copy</li>
            <li>Images (stock or AI-generated)</li>
            <li>Contact form</li>
            <li>CRM integration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Why So Fast?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Durable focuses on one thing: speed. They've optimized their AI for rapid generation without quality sacrifice.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Tradeoff</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Speed means some limitations. Durable's designs are good but not stunning. You get a working site fast, not a design masterpiece.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Speed vs Quality Tradeoff</h2>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">
          <strong>Reality:</strong> Faster generation often means simpler results. The 30-second sites are functional, not amazing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>If you need something online NOW:</strong> Choose Durable. It's the fastest "good enough" option.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>If you can wait 2-3 minutes:</strong> Squarespace or Webflow produce significantly better results.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Best approach:</strong> Generate fast with Durable, then refine and improve. Or use the slow-but-better option if time allows.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What "Fast" Actually Means</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong>30-second generation â‰  30-second launch.</strong>
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Even with Durable's 30-second generation, you'll spend time:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 ml-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Reviewing generated content (10-15 minutes)</li>
          <li>Editing and customizing (30-60 minutes)</li>
          <li>Adding your branding (15-30 minutes)</li>
          <li>Setting up custom domain (10-30 minutes)</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          <strong>Reality:</strong> Even with the fastest AI, expect 2-4 hours from start to publish-ready.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Recommendation</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>Need it TODAY:</strong> Durable. Nothing else comes close for speed.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>Have a week:</strong> Take more time. Use 10Web, Squarespace, or Webflow for better results.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Reality check:</strong> The difference between 30 seconds and 3 minutes doesn't matter much in practice. Choose based on quality, not speed.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <AffiliateCTA
        href={affiliates.durable.affiliateUrl}
        commission={affiliates.durable.commission}
        label="Try Durable (Fastest AI)"
        className="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg inline-block"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
